93.title: Precioso Asesino
93.plot: Claudio Vilches is dead and Lorena has nothing to reopen his case, in addition, the Marquez plan to leave the country to escape the scandal, but "la martillo" found out about this in time and went to face Arturo in order to get a confession. Was the real murderer discovered?

94.title: Precioso Final
94.plot: The real culprits of the death of Juan Pablo are exposed and they were condemned for their crime. Lorena managed to do justice.

imdb.title: Preciosas
plot: The story of four women who share a deep friendship, four women that happen to meet while serving time and the adventures they live after they successfully escape from jail.
